title: 057 - Tucson Sam
description: On today's show, the guys discuss what they did over the 4th of July weekend, and dive right into the Folder of Death which includes topics like whether or not eels have arms and legs, if Dunkaroos are really dead, what five condiments everyone would have come out of their fingers if those were the only condiments they could have for the rest of their lives. They also discuss what cereal mascot would win in a deathmatch with all other cereal mascots, how menacing wild turkeys are, if buffets are truly dead (unfortunately it seems like they might be), and the boys get a special drop in from the Boobz Brothers from Down Under.
